creator: robin sorder 1inde
descriptionHtml:
Hulk Skins for Minecraft is a new pack of modsthat will turn your skin into the hero of a popular superhero movie! Become a green giant and easily reach your goal in the cube world. Download skin pack - make your Minecraft Pocket Edition even more fun and colorful!

The developers constantly surprise sandbox fans with various products. This collection of skins will be especially liked by fans of comics and movies about superheroes! After all, now you can become a green giant and defeat your rivals with ease in Minecraft PE! Choose your HD quality skin. Use the animated editor 3D to view your cool image from different angles and in different locations! Tell your friends about the novelty, modificative characters together! Create a squad of invincible superheroes and become the best players in the pixel universe! This collection of skins will be interesting for both boys and girls. After all, the cinematic universe of superheroes is loved by all categories of viewers!

Forget boring and monotonous games! The cube world is a limitless space where possible to fulfill dreams and realize their creativity. You can build houses and castles anywhere in the pixel universe. Upgrade your skills: hunt different mobs and fight rivals. In this VR, you are not limited by the scope of the plot, unlike most video games! It depends only on you how the fate of your character will turn! Kids enjoy colorful gameplay, while adults forget about problems in real life!

Download maps to expand your boundaries and visit unusual locations! You can get to an amusement park, a zoo, a kingdom, an island and even a mystical village! Use every opportunity to diversify your game!

Don't miss a single app or update! Watch videos of popular youtubers to keep abreast of the latest innovations. Be a trending player! Find out more useful information on the wiki. Share your life hacks with other users, help noobs get used to virtual reality.

Hulk Skins for Minecraft DISCLAIMER: This app is not an official Minecraft app and is not affiliated with Mojang AB. This app uses assets and brands correctly in accordance with the guidelines described at https://account.mojang.com/documents/brand_guidelines

The subscription can be renewed automatically:

* For 3 days, use the free trial period, which will begin after confirmation of the payment. This time is not charged.
The subscription automatically renews once a week for $ 30.99 after the end of the trial period.

* Payment is charged to your Google Account after purchase with confirmation

* App subscription automatically renews when the trial period ends

* You can turn off the app yourself and manage your subscriptions in your account settings after making a purchase.

* Any unused time of the free period will be forfeited when purchasing a premium subscription during the trial period.

All personal data is processed in accordance with the terms of the privacy policy. More details can be found here:  https://support.google.com/googleplay/answer/7018481?co=GENIE.Platform=Android&hl=en_US
